00:05:41.560 --> 00:05:47.560
Yeah. And and really out of a lot of the scraps of material.

00:05:47.560 --> 00:05:54.560
So it was quite, it's not the case that the artists and the workers involved are well, they put themselves last.

00:05:54.560 --> 00:06:00.560
So it's only until the last few days and suddenly goes like, whoops, you know, I may have helped facilitate hundreds of costumes.

00:06:00.560 --> 00:06:02.560
And so it's like, what am I going to look like on the day?

00:06:02.600 --> 00:06:10.600
Yeah, no, because because you're not specifically with the section, you know, you've got to go around all all the different groups.

00:06:10.600 --> 00:06:12.600
Yes. Running up and down the line.

00:06:12.600 --> 00:06:14.600
So just yeah, but those were my colors.

00:06:14.600 --> 00:06:17.600
So that's why I wanted to be in that group.

00:06:17.600 --> 00:06:23.600
