00:06:38.640 --> 00:06:40.640
I was holding something to me.

00:06:40.640 --> 00:06:41.640
Oh, no, no, I wasn't.

00:06:41.640 --> 00:06:51.640
Actually, I have my ones, my pink fairy ones because because I started off before I joined the carnival.

00:06:51.640 --> 00:06:55.640
I just sort of got a performance piece up and running, which was pink fairy.

00:06:55.640 --> 00:06:57.640
Does the pink fairy still exist?

00:06:57.680 --> 00:07:03.680
She hasn't surfaced recently, but yes, she still exists.

00:07:03.680 --> 00:07:08.680
Excellent. I can see the ones in my mind's eye.

00:07:08.680 --> 00:07:13.680
And then the you had sort of like a mini feather boa wrapped around the right.

00:07:13.680 --> 00:07:21.680
So it was kind of a cross between a sort of a blue warrior type costume with my pink meets the pink fairy.

00:07:21.720 --> 00:07:22.720
Yes.

