I finished that.

00:11:01.000 --> 00:11:06.000
So 99 being the first the year I joined or 98 this year, I joined the carnival.

00:11:06.040 --> 00:11:10.040
I'm a painter is the practice I'm doing at the moment.

00:11:10.040 --> 00:11:14.040
I use a studio at home.

