But I also do beach art and I go into the environment to create artworks, land art, beach art, land art,

00:11:50.080 --> 00:11:55.080
go into schools, doing sort of willow projects.

00:11:55.080 --> 00:11:57.080
And also.

00:11:57.120 --> 00:11:58.120
And also.

